member.summary:
Sets documents for this request.
Currently supported types are:
* Dictionary<string, CPS_SimpleXML>;
* Dictionary<string, XmlElement>;
* List<string>.

Sets search query. Use can use  class functions for generating query.

This example show how to use  function to generate search query.

r.setQuery("(" + Utils.CPS_Term("predefined_term", "generated_fields/some_field") + Utils.CPS_Term(user_supplied_term, "searchable_fields/text") + ")");
